title: 'The only one of its kind in Ireland!' - Conor McGregor's rare Lamborghini towed in Dublin city centre
text:
'The only one of its kind in Ireland!' - Conor McGregor's rare Lamborghini towed in Dublin city centre Independent.ie A Lamborghini Huracan Avio dubbed "the only one of its kind in Ireland" by Conor McGregor was spotted on the back of a tow truck in Dublin city yesterday. http://www.independent.ie/sport/mma/the-only-one-of-its-kind-in-ireland-conor-mcgregors-rare-lamborghini-towed-in-dublin-city-centre-35575734.html http://www.independent.ie/incoming/article35575870.ece/78212/AUTOCROP/h342/car%20pic.jpg 
A Lamborghini Huracan Avio dubbed "the only one of its kind in Ireland" by Conor McGregor was spotted on the back of a tow truck in Dublin city yesterday. 
The Notorious posted a picture of the vehicle on his Instagram account three days ago, claiming that he is in 'the process of building a network here where we will bring multiple high end luxury motor vehicles on to Irish shores for sale and supply'. 
The image was originally tweeted by 98FM . 
McGregor is currently spending some time in his home city, and the Lamborghini was seen being towed away in the city centre yesterday. The UFC champion has posted numerous pictures of the car on social media recently.
